item.title: Notre Dame Unveils Shamrock Series Uniforms For Game Against Army At Yankee Stadium
item.description: Notre Dame unveiled its latest Shamrock Series uniforms, which are inspired by the "Four Horsemen" and will be worn against Army at Yankee Stadium on Nov. 23.
